
## kiosk mode

https://obrienlabs.net/setup-raspberry-pi-kiosk-chromium/

## rotate

rotate display:
add `display_rotate=1` (3 for 270) to /boot/config.txt

rotate input:

https://wiki.ubuntu.com/X/InputCoordinateTransformation

scripts/rpi/startup.sh

## prevent screensaver/sleeping

https://www.bitpi.co/2015/02/14/prevent-raspberry-pi-from-sleeping/

## auto startup

https://www.cyberciti.biz/tips/linux-how-to-run-a-command-when-boots-up.html

add to ~/.config/lxsession/LXDE-pi/autostart:

@sh /home/pi/carvis-proto/app/scripts/rpi/startup.sh


